{"tid":2065022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應楊潔篪和蓬佩奧會否會晤　外交部：若有消息會發布","createTime":"2020-06-15T08:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T09:59:46.000Z","uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad22d7290aeebaa51d6acc6ea6de86b69aee2860","tid":2065022,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:41:11.000Z","msg":"有報道說，美國國務卿蓬佩奧將與中共中央政治局委員、中央外事工作委員會辦公室主任楊潔篪在夏威夷會晤。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅在例行記者會回應有關提問時表示，中美外交管道保持著溝通，如果有進一步消息，中方將及時發布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532166-20200615.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532166-20200615.htm&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7pUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=cadfcb8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532166-20200615.htm&h=8132b36b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532166-20200615.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXh4aWf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXh4aWf.gif&h=efe4f86d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6bpaWh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6bpaWh.gif&h=b77b8dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加速</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb588de0e327945d74b0f8e2d582b2e0b5d7a13d","tid":2065022,"uid":291487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"姐係傾唔店啦"},{"pid":"3cee13e6736deb26146612438ee55819a3f2f28b","tid":2065022,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb588de0e327945d74b0f8e2d582b2e0b5d7a13d","tid":2065022,"uid":291487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"姐係傾唔店啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyT